-Pull Wordpress Project from git
-Run Following Command:
	- wp core download
	- wp core download --skip-content (In Linux/Ubuntu)

-Configuration of wp-config.php file
	- cp wp-config-sample.php wp-config.php
	- Change Database Values
		- Database-User-Name
		- Database-Password

-Create Virtual_host to the Project Folder before-Wp-Content Directory
-Make entry in the /etc/hosts File
-Run Search and Replace
-$ wp search-replace 'foo' 'bar' wp_posts wp_postmeta wp_terms --dry-run

-update links (Wp-options)
